				<wikidot:authorName>DrBleep</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2887044</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't know what I expected when I opened this page, but it definitely wasn't this. You manage to capture a lot here, but 300 Brights and 096 as a temporary bright took the insanity boat, turned it upside down, shook it to pieces, and then rebuilt it again into a functional monster.</p> <p>The best part wasn't even the brights taking over the site. It was fucking Clef walking into the site, realizing what happened, and <em>pretending</em> to be Bright as well and then fucking with Troy. I've never seen something so in character. +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
